      "writtenOn": "2020-04-18T15:20:46Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "for a reader, unclear what IPC this is talking about. perhaps we need to add a link to the protocol description. i think sink package godoc would be a good place, and then we can put a link here.\n\nnot for this CL, so let\u0027s just add a TODO",
